&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/2336202/1627461223570-5f872b38-0072-4b5c-843b-8c8848fdeff1.png&#34; alt=&#34;img&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
